ass=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防員將火救熄。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236316/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b0dd87ac3e294917d1ec7c1c59ddd86/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_110623589_03_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236317/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3246d276b6c2bbe6d0706572e29a002/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_110623589_04_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236318/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27b5c13601ce996726b013f82cb51e9c/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_110623589_05_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-